17 June, with 6 verified transits recorded across the monitored zone. @Kpler #OOTT", "time": "08:37", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 48547, "likes": 173, "replies": 12, "retweets": 36, "quotes": 4, "bookmarks": 8, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2067527848253116459", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2067527848253116459", "text": "Do you want to know what will spoil the deal?? THIS: Senior Israeli official: Despite the MOU, the IDF will not withdraw from southern Lebanon.  #OOTT", "time": "08:40", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 18187, "likes": 136, "replies": 14, "retweets": 26, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2067528197512495462", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2067528197512495462", "text": "Hormuz normalization to take months - Lloyd's market association #oott", "time": "08:41", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 4249, "likes": 39, "replies": 3, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2067528491117969765", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2067528491117969765", "text": "#Singapore: oil product inventories rose by 0.850mb w/w to 35.258mb last week #oott", "time": "08:42", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 11051, "likes": 40, "replies": 0, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2067552436068262218", "url": "https://x.com